snippet.title: Rollcage Trailer (feat. Fatboy Slim)
snippet.description:
Fast as hell.

This was definitely one of the most fun destruction race games since Activision's Death Track Racing. Fatboy Slim made some royalties on this one. I believe this game did better in Europe than in North America.

And um.. see anything wrong with that kick?
